{
  "stem": "25348.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When I returned-- you see, I had no perception of curfew, not curfew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "I had to see my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And on my way back, I sort of lied down in snow and cried.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I had no adult sort of advice what to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "When I got back to the Todt building-- because they provided dormitory for its workers-- a torch, someone shone a torch into my eyes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And I told you before about these German supervisors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "It was one of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] beginning of winter, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] there was snow and rain.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My face must have been flushed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all he wanted to know, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who beat you up?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was a child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And his name was Paul Moebius, M-O-E-B-I-U-S.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was always kind [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And of course, I was there as a Pole, not as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was-- I secured this job as a Polish girl, not a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I confessed to him, when he kept pestering me, how come you're here at this time?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a curfew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're not allowed to be out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I told him, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he looked at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I could see some pity in his eyes, but I couldn't get into the man's mind.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, all he said to me, go to bed, child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I reached my cot, I thought to myself, I was stupid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What were you looking for?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For a father figure?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where is your mother?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Is she in heaven?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In a grave?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
